      "content": "interesting. so if the main argument is that it helps people in the long run, how do you reconcile that with the fact that it's basically an immediate extra cost for people who have no choice but to drive for work, like tradespeople or delivery drivers? it seems like a pretty heavy burden to place on them right away.",
